						               													<description>MasterMinds is a GAME OF DEDUCTION where in order to determine who the MasterMind is, what they're like and where they are, you need to make your way around the board and ask the right questions of the other players using your deductive reasoning skills and the process of elimination, trying to be the first to solve the mystery of who and where the MasterMind is and climb their steps to knock on their door.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In a standard game, each player holds three cards, Description, Character and Place. The remaining 3 cards for the round are the MasterMind's cards. With the occasional advantage or disadvantage of Bonuses and Penalties players make their way around the board Asking Questions and Taking Notes using their Solver Pad until they're ready to Climb The Steps to Make Their Guess and find out if they're at the MasterMinds Door!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Is the MasterMind a Lonely Zombie In Your Closet, a Kind Grandma At The Grocery Store, a Frustrated Time Traveler In The Woods???...It could be anyone, anywhere, IT'S TIME TO PLAY AND FIGURE IT OUT!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
